 cloudy skies and moderate temperatures - and will end with a light show.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two thirds\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"daylight\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather forecast\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"cloudy skies\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"moderate temperatures\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"a light show\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The music will be a mix of classical, traditional 'chanson francaise', as well as rap and electro.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_dance_music\", \"score\": 0.9999958690644974, \"rank\": 3.679071273389325e-06, \"text\": \"electro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_dance_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_dance_music\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The music\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"a mix\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"classical, traditional 'chanson francaise\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"rap\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Franco-Malian R&B star Aya Nakamura is set to be one of the star performers despite criticism from far-right politicians, including Marine Le Pen, who suggested in March that an appearance by her would \\\"humiliate\\\" France.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2261, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhythm_and_blues\", \"score\": 0.9999815984080304, \"rank\": 1.8401812131050312e-05, \"text\": \"R&B\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhythm_and_blues\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp