, \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 2522, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6561041911525843e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rumours\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French electro superstars Daft Punk have turned down an invitation to play, while globe-trotting French DJ David Guetta has been overlooked - much to his irritation.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daft_Punk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3348917004857926e-14, \"text\": \"Daft Punk\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daft_Punk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daft_Punk\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9809112535286447, \"rank\": 0.018464923721846334, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Guetta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Guetta\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Guetta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Guetta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an invitation\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"his irritation\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked to sum up his message last week, Jolly said it was \\\"love.\\\"\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mes