 0.018464923721846334, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"the widely panned retro-styled opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3204}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's rugby World Cup\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"a succession\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"baguettes\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3297}, {\"ngram\": \"berets\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And do not expect a three-hour tribute to French greatness to rival the nationalistic pageantry seen at the Beijing Games in 2008.\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3373, \"end\": 3379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9809112535286447, \"rank\": 0.018464923721846334, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three-hour tribute\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"the nationalistic pageantry\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The opening ceremony in Beijing in 2008 was exactly what we did not want to do,\\\" Boucheron toldLe Mondenewspaper.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3488, \"end\": 3495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9217868677811463, \"rank\": 0.08484946079558703, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 